NEEDS >TAPE  tape
NEEDS S"     strings

: /SAVET  ( n1 n2 -- )
  \ Save the Forth RAM-disk to tape,
  \ from screen n1 to screen n2.
  \ n1 = first screen
  \ n2 = last screen
  FLUSH 1+ DISC-SCR SWAP DISC-SCR
  DUP ROT SWAP -  S" DISC" >TAPE  ;

  \ vim: filetype=abersoftforthafera
